snippet: Prime Minister David Cameron of Britain said Monday that he found some elements of the Syrian opposition worrying, as Russia warned against arming the rebels.
lead_paragraph: Prime Minister David Cameron of Britain said Monday that he found some elements of the Syrian opposition worrying, as Russia warned against arming the rebels.

headline.main: Syria and Russia Warn West Against Aiding Rebels
